org.apache.beam.sdk.io.aws.sns

Interface AwsClientsProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface AwsClientsProvider
extends java.io.Serializable
    Provides instances of AWS clients.

    Please note, that any instance of AwsClientsProvider must be Serializable to ensure it can be sent to worker machines.
